channel.title: How do I add TzTok Jad and the fight caves?
channel.description: The question is in the title. I have the fight caves in my server but when I started working on it, while the caves teled you to the inside, the waves dont spawn and idk how to make them spawn.

item.title: How do I add TzTok Jad and the fight caves?
item.dc:creator: @Dark_Armed Dark Armed
item.description:
@Dark_Armed wrote:

Acutally I found a tutorial on how to spawn him, played with it a little and I have 1 problem. When you go into the caves he wont spawn. If you log out and back in he does though.

More importantly I have a huge issue. His melee is supposed to be instant damage, his range and mage are supposed to be delayed. However his range is instant too. I dont know how to fix lol.

item.title: How do I add TzTok Jad and the fight caves?
item.dc:creator: @Trxkin Trxkin
item.description:
@Trxkin wrote:

Go to your server>config.java. Then go to autospawn.cfg. Once there. Find the coords you want the Jad to be at, and put in there somehting like thisâ€¦

spawn = 2745 X Y 0 0 0 0 0 1
